---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "~/components/breadcrumbs.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import svg1 from "~/assets/SprintingDoodle.svg";
import services from "~/data/service/services.json";
import Btn from "~/components/button.astro";
const urlList = Astro.url.pathname.split("/").filter(Boolean);
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="mt-20 sm:mt-10 sm:pb-32 sm:pt-10">
    <Breadcrumbs urlList={urlList} />
    <ContentSection title="我们的服务" subtitle="Our Service" id="service">
      <Fragment slot="description">
        我们提供包括品牌策略制定、视觉识别系统设计、包装设计、互动体验设计以及环境导视系统等在内的全方位品牌设计服务。Greener-Dalii
        Studio以敏锐的洞察力和深厚的专业技能，助您塑造独特且持久的品牌影响力。
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="description-below">
        We offer a full spectrum of branding services, ranging from brand
        strategy formulation, visual identity systems, packaging design,
        interactive experience design to environmental signage systems. At
        Greener-Dalii Studio, we leverage sharp insights and deep expertise to
        forge distinctive and enduring brand impressions.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="content">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-5">
          <div class="col-span-full md:col-span-3 md:col-start-3">
            <!-- capsules -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              {
                services.map((service) => (
                  <span class="group relative cursor-default rounded-full border border-[--color-text-offset] px-8 py-2 hover:bg-[--color-primary]">
                    <span class="block font-normal transition-opacity duration-300 ease-in-out text-xs group-hover:opacity-0 sm:text-base">
                      {service.en}
                    </span>
                    <span class="absolute left-0 top-0 block w-full min-w-max pt-2 text-center font-normal opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 ease-in-out text-xs group-hover:opacity-100 sm:text-base">
                      {service.zh}
                    </span>
                  </span>
                ))
              }
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col py-20">
              <div class="font-normal text-lg">我们提供两种服务模式 🎉</div>
              <div class="font-light text-sm">We offer two service models</div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-8 sm:gap-x-8">
                <div class="indicator w-full sm:w-auto">
                  <span
                    class="badge indicator-item badge-sm bg-[--color-primary]"
                    >推荐</span
                  >
                  <Btn
                    btnText="设计订阅制"
                    btnAltText="Subscription"
                    url="#subscription"
                    cls="px-6"
                  />
                </div>
                <Btn
                  btnText="按项目付费制"
                  btnAltText="Pay-Per-Project"
                  url="#pay-per-project"
                  cls="px-6"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- subscription -->
        <section id="subscription">
          <div
            class="mx-auto flex flex-col flex-wrap pt-32 sm:flex-row sm:pt-24"
          >
            <div class="mb-2 flex flex-col md:w-2/5">
              <h4 class="title-font text-left font-normal text-2xl">
                设计订阅制<span class="badge badge-lg bg-[--color-primary]"
                  >推荐！</span
                >
              </h4>
              <h5
                class="mb-5 text-left font-normal text-base sm:mb-0 sm:text-lg"
              >
                Design Subscription Plan
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div class="flex w-full flex-col text-left md:w-3/5">
              <p class="mb-5 break-words leading-loose text-default">
                受互联网行业SaaS范式的启发，我们推出创新的<span
                  class="inline-block font-medium">「设计订阅制」</span
                >服务。您只需支付固定订阅费用，即可享受无限量的设计服务请求，并且可随时<span
                  class="inline-block font-medium">暂停或取消</span
                >计划。
              </p>
              <p class="mb-5 break-words leading-loose text-default">
                它改变了传统按项目收费的方式，您无需为每个单独的设计项目支付费用，加入我们的订阅计划，就如同拥有了一个高质量的专属设计团队。无论是日常宣传素材、新产品包装设计、还是品牌升级，我们都将按您的需求精心设计，直至您满意为止。
              </p>
              <p class="mb-5 break-words leading-relaxed text-default text-sm">
                Inspired by SaaS, we've created the <span
                  class="inline-block font-medium">Design Subscription</span
                >. One flat fee unlocks unlimited design tasks, pause or cancel
                anytime.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-5 break-words leading-relaxed text-default text-sm">
                No more per-project costs. Subscribe and have a top-notch design
                team at your fingertips. We'll meticulously craft every
                request—from daily ads to product packaging and brand
                evolution—until it meets your satisfaction.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mx-auto py-12 sm:py-24">
            <div class="relative grid grid-cols-5">
              <div
                class="absolute col-span-2 hidden md:bottom-1/3 md:right-2/3 md:block"
              >
                <Icon
                  name="service/SprintingDoodle"
                  class="h-96 w-96 sm:h-[40rem] sm:w-[40rem]"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-full md:col-span-3 md:col-start-3">
                <div
                  class="mds:gap-8 grid grid-cols-2 content-around justify-stretch justify-items-stretch gap-4 pb-12 md:grid-cols-3"
                >
                  <div
                    class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-lg bg-[--color-background-offset] px-4 py-8"
                  >
                    <Icon
                      name="service/fixed"
                      class="text-[--color-text] transition-all text-5xl group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div class="text-center text-xs">
                      固定费率<br />成本可控，预算友好<br />Fixed fee, Easy
                      budgeting
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-lg bg-[--color-background-offset] px-4 py-8"
                  >
                    <Icon
                      name="service/brilliant"
                      class="transition-all text-5xl group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div class="text-center text-xs">
                      高品质设计，专业审美<br />确保视觉一致性<br />Premium
                      designs, Cohesive visuals
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-lg bg-[--color-background-offset] px-4 py-8"
                  >
                    <Icon
                      name="service/pause"
                      class="transition-all text-5xl group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div class="text-center text-xs">
                      灵活高效<br />随时暂停，节省支出<br />Pause anytime, Save
                      costs
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-lg bg-[--color-background-offset] px-4 py-8"
                  >
                    <Icon
                      name="service/queue"
                      class="transition-all text-5xl group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div class="text-center text-xs">
                      队列流程管理<br />订阅期设计请求不限量<br />Unlimited
                      requests via queue
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-lg bg-[--color-background-offset] px-4 py-8"
                  >
                    <Icon
                      name="service/fast"
                      class="transition-all text-5xl group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div class="text-center text-xs">
                      敏捷设计，快速交付<br />Rapid design, Quick delivery
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-4 rounded-lg bg-[--color-background-offset] px-4 py-8"
                  >
                    <Icon
                      name="service/satisfy"
                      class="transition-all text-5xl group-hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div class="text-center text-xs">
                      修改至100%满意<br />Tweaks until fully satisfied
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 py-12">
                  <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-between gap-4">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                      <div class="font-normal text-lg">还有一些问题？</div>
                      <div class="font-light text-sm">Any questions?</div>
                    </div>
                    <Btn
                      btnText="看看这里 👀"
                      btnAltText="Look Here 👀"
                      url="#faq"
                      cls="px-6"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-between gap-4">
                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                      <div class="font-normal text-lg">
                        联系我们开始订阅服务 📃
                      </div>
                      <div class="font-light text-sm">
                        Contact us to start subscribing
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <Btn
                      btnText="联系我们 👋"
                      btnAltText="Contact Us 👋"
                      url="/contact"
                      cls="px-6"
                    />
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <!-- PPP -->
        <section id="pay-per-project">
          <div
            class="mx-auto flex flex-col flex-wrap pt-32 sm:flex-row sm:pt-24"
          >
            <div class="mb-2 flex flex-col md:w-2/5">
              <h4 class="title-font text-left font-normal text-2xl">
                按项目付费制
              </h4>
              <h5
                class="mb-5 text-left font-normal text-base sm:mb-0 sm:text-lg"
              >
                Pay-Per-Project Plan
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div class="flex w-full flex-col text-left md:w-3/5">
              <p class="lleading-loose break-words text-default">
                如果您与我们是初次合作，或对订阅制比较陌生，也可以采用按项目付费形式。
              </p>
              <p class="mt-5 break-words leading-relaxed text-default text-sm">
                If you're working with us for the first time, or are new to the
                subscription system, a pay-per-project format is also available.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mx-auto py-12 sm:py-24">
            <div class="relative grid grid-cols-5">
              <div
                class="absolute col-span-2 hidden md:-bottom-72 md:right-2/3 md:block"
              >
                <Icon
                  name="service/GroovySittingDoodle"
                  class="h-96 w-96 sm:h-[40rem] sm:w-[40rem]"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="col-span-full md:col-span-3 md:col-start-3">
                <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-between gap-4">
                  <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <div class="font-normal text-lg">
                      联系我们获取项目报价单 📃
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-light text-sm">
                      Contact us for the project quotation
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <Btn
                    btnText="联系我们 👋"
                    btnAltText="Contact Us 👋"
                    url="/contact"
                    cls="px-6"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <!-- FAQs -->
        <section id="faq">
          <div
            class="mx-auto flex flex-col flex-wrap pt-32 sm:flex-row sm:pt-24"
          >
            <div class="mb-2 flex flex-col md:w-2/5">
              <h4 class="title-font text-left font-normal text-2xl">
                还有疑问？
              </h4>
              <h5
                class="mb-5 text-left font-normal text-base sm:mb-0 sm:text-lg"
              >
                FAQs about Subscription
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div class="flex w-full flex-col text-left md:w-3/5">
              <div class="grid gap-y-2">
                <!-- requests -->
                <div
                  class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-[--color-background-offset]"
                >
                  <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-3" />
                  <div class="collapse-title font-medium text-base">
                    我能提出多少设计需求都可以吗？
                    <h4 class="text-xs">
                      Can I submit as many design requests as I want?
                    </h4>
                  </div>
                  <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p class="text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      没有限制，您可以根据实际需求，随时将任何数量的设计需求加入工作队列，我们会一一为您完成。
                    </p>
                    <p class="pt-3 text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      Absolutely, no limits. Add any number of design tasks to
                      your queue as needed, and we'll tackle them one by one.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Delivery -->
                <div
                  class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-[--color-background-offset]"
                >
                  <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-3" />
                  <div class="collapse-title font-medium text-base">
                    我的设计需求能够多快交付？
                    <h4 class="text-xs">
                      How promptly can I expect my designs to be delivered?
                    </h4>
                  </div>
                  <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p class="text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      一般的设计需求，我们通常将在两个工作日内高效完成。但更为复杂的需求可能需要更长的时问周期。以下为各类设计项目的预估平均交付时间（注：此时长是根据历史经验统计而来，实际可能存在波动）
                    </p>
                    <p class="pt-3 text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      We typically fulfill standard requests within two business
                      days. More complex ones may require additional time.The
                      following are the estimated average delivery times for
                      various types of design projects (note: these times are
                      based on historical experience and may fluctuate in
                      reality)
                    </p>
                    <table class="table table-auto mt-5">
                      <thead>
                        <tr>
                          <th class="text-xs">项目 | Project</th>
                          <th class="text-xs">平均交付时间 | Average Time</th>
                        </tr>
                      </thead>
                      <tbody>
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">Banner（一系列）</td>
                          <td class="text-xs">1~3 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">包装设计 | Packaging Design</td>
                          <td class="text-xs">2~5 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">宣传海报（每张） | Each Poster</td
                          >
                          <td class="text-xs">2~7 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                        
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">网页（单页面）| Single Webpage</td
                          >
                          <td class="text-xs">5~10 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">宣传画册 | IP Design</td>
                          <td class="text-xs">5~15 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">LOGO</td>
                          <td class="text-xs">5~20 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">IP设计 | IP Design</td>
                          <td class="text-xs">5~20 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td class="text-xs">VI设计 | Brand VI</td>
                          <td class="text-xs">10~60 Days</td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Don't like -->
                <div
                  class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-[--color-background-offset]"
                >
                  <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-3" />
                  <div class="collapse-title font-medium text-base">
                    如果对设计方案不太满意怎么办？
                    <h4 class="text-xs">What if I don't like the design?</h4>
                  </div>
                  <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p class="text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      不用担心！我们将继续修改设计，直到您 100% 满意为止。
                    </p>
                    <p class="pt-3 text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      No worries! We'll continue to revise the design until
                      you're 100% satisfied.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Pause -->
                <div
                  class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-[--color-background-offset]"
                >
                  <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-3" />
                  <div class="collapse-title font-medium text-base">
                    订阅制暂停功能怎么使用？
                    <h4 class="text-xs">
                      How does the pause feature work in subscription?
                    </h4>
                  </div>
                  <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p class="text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      我们理解您可能会在某些时候暂时没有新的设计需求。因此，订阅服务提供了灵活的暂停机制，让您可以暂停服务并保留剩余时长，待有新需求时再继续。
                    </p>
                    <p class="pt-3 text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      Recognizing downtime in needs, the pause option allows you
                      to halt service, preserving your subscription length for
                      future use.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- One requests -->
                <div
                  class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-[--color-background-offset]"
                >
                  <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-3" />
                  <div class="collapse-title font-medium text-base">
                    如果我只有一个请求项目怎么办？
                    <h4 class="text-xs">
                      What if I only have a single request?
                    </h4>
                  </div>
                  <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p class="text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      没关系，完成该需求后，您可以使用上面所说的暂停功能，等下次有新需求再继续。我们不希望您为剩余未用的时长付费。
                    </p>
                    <p class="pt-3 text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      No problem. Use the pause feature post-completion, and
                      resume when new needs arise. We don't want you to pay for
                      unused time.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Refund -->
                <div
                  class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-[--color-background-offset]"
                >
                  <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-3" />
                  <div class="collapse-title font-medium text-base">
                    如果我不喜欢这项服务，可以退款吗？
                    <h4 class="text-xs">
                      Are there any refunds if I don't like the service?
                    </h4>
                  </div>
                  <div class="collapse-content">
                    <p class="text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      鉴于我们为每一项设计付出的高强度精力，如当月已有执行项目时，很抱歉订阅费将不予退还，您可以随时取消下个月订阅服务即可。
                    </p>
                    <p class="pt-3 text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                      Considering the intensive effort per design, refunds
                      aren't available once work is underway for the month, but
                      you can cancel future months.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Track -->
                <div
                  class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-[--color-background-offset]"
                >
                  <input type="radio" name="my-accordion-3" />
                  <div class="collapse-title font-medium text-base">
                    你们如何管理项目？我们如何追踪任务进度？
                    <h4 class="text-xs">
                      How do you manage projects and track progress?
                    </h4>
                  </div>
                  <div class="collapse-content">
                    <div
                      class="flex flex-col content-center justify-items-stretch gap-8 sm:flex-row"
                    >
                      <div class="basis-3/4">
                        <p class="text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                          我们基于飞书搭建了一套业务管理系统，您可轻松掌握查看实时的任务队列和进度情况，也可查询订阅剩余时问。您可以用飞书扫描二维码查看我们的示例
                        </p>
                        <p class="pt-3 text-[--color-text-offset] text-xs">
                          Leveraging Feishu, we've established a streamlined
                          system. You can effortlessly monitor real-time task
                          queues, progress, and remaining subscription time.
                          Scan the QR code with Feishu for a demo.
                        </p>
                      </div>
                      <Icon
                        name="service/streamline"
                        class="h-28 w-28 grow basis-1/4 text-[--color-text-offset]"
                      />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-between gap-4 pt-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                  <div class="font-normal text-lg">需要进一步的沟通 🙋‍♂️</div>
                  <div class="font-light text-sm">Further communication</div>
                </div>
                <Btn
                  btnText="联系我们 👋"
                  btnAltText="Contact Us 👋"
                  url="/contact"
                  cls="px-6"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </Fragment>
    </ContentSection>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
